San Cristobal
New Mexico.        
8.( )
Dear Mr Anderson,
Thank you for your very
kind letters of May 7th, 
which has caught up with
me at last, after much forwarding, 
in New Mexico.
We passed through New
( ) in front of schedule —
So your letter had to follow.
It is very kind of you
to suggest that we should
stop and see you in Virginia.
Unfortunately there is no
prospect of our being anywhere
near Virginia for a number
of months. But I hope

Very much that an 
opportunity will present
itself before very log
of accepting your invitation.
Yours very sincerely 
Aldous Huxley .
